CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 9, 1958, pg. A15, reads: "FROGS" Guests - Getting a bang out of the annual Frog formal held at Gateway Plaza... - Teenie Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of FROGS members including Buddy Leftwich, Wendell Freeland in front, Mr. Fraser in center, and Morris Fountain Sr., Linn Washington fifth from left, Bill Frederick, and Judge Henry Smith in back, posed in front of bandstand in Gateway Plaza
